'''唐麗球'''（{{lang-en|Joan Tong Lai Kau}}，{{bd|1964年|6月16日|catIdx=T唐}}），綽號“波波”，1984年參與[[香港小姐競選|香港小姐競選]]奪得季軍。她的[[姨甥女|姨甥女]][[嘉碧儀|嘉碧儀]]是2002年度香港小姐競選最後5強。

==背景==
唐麗球祖籍[[浙江|浙江]][[寧波|寧波]]，有四名胞兄胞姊{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}<ref>{{cite news | title=唐麗球復出螢幕 為亞視演出劇集 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%94%90%E9%BA%97%E7%90%83&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJEplJWG75lpk&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=126&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%94%90%E9%BA%97%E7%90%83%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%94%90%E9%BA%97%E7%90%83%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%94%90%E9%BA%97%E7%90%83%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%94%90%E9%BA%97%E7%90%83%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%94%90%E9%BA%97%E7%90%83%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%94%90%E9%BA%97%E7%90%83%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | page=18 | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1989-05-08| accessdate=2020-12-06|quote= }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=唐麗球獲無綫批准 提早赴英探望兄長 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%94%90%E9%BA%97%E7%90%83&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58Sngm8Qm6MnxRCxfida6tf&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=52&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%94%90%E9%BA%97%E7%90%83%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%94%90%E9%BA%97%E7%90%83%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%94%90%E9%BA%97%E7%90%83%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%94%90%E9%BA%97%E7%90%83%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%94%90%E9%BA%97%E7%90%83%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%94%90%E9%BA%97%E7%90%83%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | page=19 | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1984-09-01| accessdate=2020-12-06|quote= }}</ref>，父親是一名海員{{noteTag|name=守下留情1|關於唐麗球父親職